          "TITLE": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "-PROMPT GAMMA-RAYS FROM NEUTRON INTERACTION IN U-235",
                " AND RESONANCE SPIN ASSIGNMENTS.-"
              ]
            }
          ],
          "FACILITY": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": {
                "facility": [
                  "LINAC"
                ],
                "institute": null
              },
              "free_text": [
                "    CBNM ELECTRON LINEAR ACCELERATOR."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "INC-SOURCE": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                ".PHOTO NEUTRONS FROM A NATURAL URANIUM TARGET",
                " MODERATED BY A POLYETHYLENE SLAB."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "SAMPLE": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                ".METALLIC SAMPLE, 200 MG/CM2.",
                ".ISOTOPIC COMPOSITION 93 PER-CENT  U-235."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "METHOD": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "TOF"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                "      TIME OF FLIGHT, FLIGHT-PATH = 8.3 M."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "DETECTOR": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "GELI"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                "     GERMANIUM-LITHIUM DETECTOR.",
                ".NEUTRON TIME OF FLIGHT AND GAMMA-RAY ENERGY WERE",
                " RECORDED SIMULTANEOUSLY."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "ANALYSIS": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                ".BY LOOKING AT AN RESONANCE WITH LARGE ALPHA (MAINLY",
                " CAPTURE) 6.4 EV, AND WITH SMALL ALPHA (MAINLY FISSION)",
                " 8.8 EV, THE CAPTURE AND FISSION GAMMA S COULD BE",
                " SEPARATED.",
                ".THE INTENSITY OF THE 642 KEV CAPTURE LINE (FROM THE",
                " 687 KEV 2- LEVEL TO THE 45 KEV 2+ FIRST EXCITED STATE",
                " OF U-236) RELATIVE TO THE CAPTURE PART OF THE GAMMA-",
                " RAY SPECTRUM ABOVE A CERTAIN THRESHOLD HAS BEEN",
                " MEASURED FOR EACH RESONANCE. THE RELATIVE RESULT IS",
                " INSENSITIVE FOR THE VALUE OF THE THRESHOLD.",
                ".TWO GROUPS ONE WITH LARGE RATIO (SPIN-PARITY = 3-)",
                " AND WITH SMALL RATIO (SPIN-PARITY 4-) EMERGE."
              ]
            }
          ],
